WEBVTT

00:10:27.432 --> 00:10:30.316
Am I right in saying that Islam
means "submission"?

00:10:30.822 --> 00:10:32.558
DM: It does.

00:10:32.582 --> 00:10:36.470
You could say "submission," "surrender,"
"devotion to God," yes.

00:10:36.494 --> 00:10:38.679
CA: So that's right at the heart of it.

00:10:38.703 --> 00:10:43.945
And so there was this moment where
this proud -- can I say confident? --

00:10:43.969 --> 00:10:48.020
young woman who was fighting for feminism

00:10:48.044 --> 00:10:54.074
reached this point through this belief
in this idea that she could surrender,

00:10:54.098 --> 00:10:55.277
submit to God,

00:10:55.301 --> 00:10:59.180
and in so doing, claim
a different kind of feminist identity,

00:10:59.204 --> 00:11:00.998
as well as many other --